glossary.name: hyoomie
glossary.text: Slang for humans. The first choice when it comes to meat consumption on the planet Loduwn
glossary.title: Hyoomies

glossary.name: gyoomie
glossary.text: Slang for Gomyans. I fine meat delicacy prized on the planet Loduwn. Doesn't pair very well with hyoomie meat.
glossary.title: Gyoomies
